===Etymology===
Attested late, in ''{{w|Shiming}}'' as {{lang|zh|柂}} <!-- 《四部叢刊初編》 /《欽定四庫全書》本 / 古今逸史 --> and ''{{w|Guangyun}}'' as {{lang|zh|舵}}.

''Shiming'' connects it to {{och-l|拖|tr=*l̥ˤaj|to drag, to pull, to haul}}<!-- 其尾曰柂，柂，拖也，後見拖曳也。且弼正船，使順流，不使他戾也。 -->. Meanwhile, {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} considers it an {{w|Mainland Southeast Asia linguistic area|areal}} word; compare {{cog|vi|lái||to drive (a wheeled vehicle), to steer (a vessel), etc.}} and {{cog|th|ท้าย||stern; back; rear end}}.

